 :tx/rationale "BEDROCK: Braid is infrastructure for organizational learning. The atomic operation at every level of the system is the same: observe reality, compare to model, reduce the discrepancy. Datom assertion, boundary evaluation, gradient routing, weight calibration, structure discovery, and ontology discovery are all instances of this one operation at different levels of abstraction. The 8-type divergence taxonomy is a complete enumeration of the ways a model can diverge from reality. If you detect and reduce all 8, the model converges toward truth. The product is not a tool for software coherence. It is infrastructure for the progressive, empirical, closed-loop reduction of divergence between what an organization believes and what is actually true about its domain."
